observationText: The SK-MEL-217 cell line expressed high levels of activated RAS, including both GTP-bound KRAS and NRAS, likely due to loss of NF1 expression. It harbored KRAS gene amplification.
The SK-MEL-217 cell line exhibited copy number gain of the KRAS gene locus on chromosome 17.
The SK-MEL-217 cell line was found to have complete loss of NF1 expression.
